FLAT Reference File
-------------------

:REFTYPE: FLAT
:Data model: `~stdatamodels.jwst.datamodels.FlatModel`

The FLAT reference file contains pixel-by-pixel detector response values.
It is used for all instrument modes except the NIRSpec spectroscopic modes.

